---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About" 
  description="Learn about Aaron Brown and Zelnot's approach to technology consulting."
>
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-slate-800 to-slate-900 text-white section-padding">
    <div class="container-tight">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
        About
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-2xl">
        Independent technology consulting built on expertise, transparency, and genuine partnership.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="container-tight">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">
            Aaron Brown, Principal Consultant
          </h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-slate-600">
            <p>
              I'm a technology consultant based near Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania, focused on helping 
              businesses navigate the complex world of software development and operations.
            </p>
            <p>
              My practice centers on three core areas: building custom software solutions, 
              integrating disparate systems, and implementing DevOps practices that enable teams 
              to deliver value faster and more reliably.
            </p>
            <p>
              What sets independent consulting apart is the direct relationship. You work with me, 
              not a rotating cast of junior consultants. I bring full ownership and accountability 
              to every engagement.
            </p>
            <p>
              I serve clients ranging from early-stage startups to established enterprises, 
              across industries including healthcare, manufacturing, finance, insurance, retail, 
              and education. This breadth gives me perspective that narrow specialists can't offer.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">My Approach</h3>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Listen First</h4>
              <p class="text-slate-600">
                Before recommending solutions, I invest time understanding your business context, 
                constraints, and goals.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Practical Solutions</h4>
              <p class="text-slate-600">
                I focus on what works, not what's trendy. The best solution is one your team 
                can actually implement and maintain.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Knowledge Transfer</h4>
              <p class="text-slate-600">
                My goal is to leave your team stronger, not dependent. I document thoroughly 
                and ensure you have the understanding to move forward independently.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Transparent Communication</h4>
              <p class="text-slate-600">
                Regular updates, honest assessments, and clear expectations throughout every project.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding bg-slate-50">
    <div class="container-tight">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8 text-center">
        Technical Focus Areas
      </h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        {[
          { 
            title: 'Languages & Frameworks',
            items: ['Python', 'JavaScript/TypeScript', 'Node.js', '.NET/C#', 'Go', 'Rust', 'C', 'C++', 'Java']
          },
          { 
            title: 'Cloud & Infrastructure',
            items: ['AWS', 'Azure', 'Google Cloud', 'Kubernetes', 'Terraform', 'Docker', 'Private Cloud']
          },
          { 
            title: 'Data & Integration',
            items: ['Microsoft SQL Server', 'PostgreSQL', 'Redis', 'Kafka', 'REST APIs', 'GraphQL', 'ETL Pipelines']
          },
          { 
            title: 'DevOps & Automation',
            items: ['GitHub Actions', 'GitLab CI', 'Jenkins', 'Prometheus', 'Grafana', 'Ansible', 'Nagios', 'Solarwinds']
          }
        ].map(category => (
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-4">{category.title}</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              {category.items.map(item => (
                <li class="text-slate-600 text-sm">{item}</li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="container-tight text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">
        Let's Work Together
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        I'm always interested in hearing about new projects and opportunities. 
        Whether you have a specific need or just want to explore possibilities, reach out.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary text-lg px-8 py-4">
        Get in Touch
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
